data.description: Owner Financing available, Ready to start living on lake time? This comfy 3 Bed/ 2 Bath located on Parkside Loop just off of Lake Shore Dr in beautiful Rayburn Country is ready to become your temporary or permanent address! This property features an open concept living area with vaulted ceilings in the living/dining space and a spacious kitchen that walks into the utility/Mud room from the garage. A split floor plan gives the master suite with en-suite bath privacy from the 2 additional bedrooms. Walk-out onto the covered porch or spend evenings dining on the patio deck overlooking to the yard with access to a seasonal creek! Whether you're here for the summer, weekend or year round, you're sure to get all the best of Rayburn's southern community with quick access to multiple boat ramps, restaurants, shopping, storage facilities and the Angelina River/National Forest; you are bound to find rest, relaxation and your 'home sweet home.'
